,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"睇嚟係我諗多咗<br />\n扮下野氹都無<br />\n都係繼續用酒精麻醉自己算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d62bb816436e026d74a08171df2e226363b52a","tid":1671274,"uid":33491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:34:19.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以氹返我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdd2a50b21e4fd963e82436fc522a374fabea87","tid":1671274,"uid":33491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:47:58.000Z","msg":"被你浪費 被你活埋<br />\n讓你愉快 讓我瓦解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23faebf2aae6bf68aaa637ff7d290c6a78628b5e","tid":1671274,"uid":33491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"定係我唔值得你哂時間去氹"},{"pid":"feb77683982f0b002a8933b66e5c6a59109340a6","tid":1671274,"uid":33491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"嘔完之後成個人心情舒暢好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e30596a54fd085be8428a08674827dd077fa844","tid":1671274,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2574a16b9a34f8ce314e56e83419b9b52caac151","tid":1671274,"uid":33491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"自己無錢無家底無學歷無錢無高度無樣<br />\n個人又無自信<br />\n越嚟越多負能量<br />\n<br />\n點解我唔開心嗰陣<br />\n無人可以氹下我<br />\n我唔開心就等於發緊你脾氣?<br />\n態度唔好？<br />\n我都想有人氹呀<br />\n定係做人男朋友就唔可以唔開心呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呻完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=4cbe38a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}